pageContext.claim: “I think it's very clear that there are people in your profession that write fake news. You do. She does. There are people in your profession that write fake news. They would love to see me, for whatever reason -- because we've done one hell of a job. Nobody has done the job that we've done.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump calls news reports that he does not find favorable to be "fake news." But mainstream news organizations do not invent articles out of whole cloth.
